metadata.name: Landscape_A11
metadata.description:
How often do people realize themselves on the surface of the planet, which is moving in the vast space at a speed of 29,765 km/s? 
This is an incredible feeling that rarely visits us because of the familiarity of everything that surrounds us. 
This collection allows you to experience it in a new way, demonstrating fragments of our planet through the prism of involvement in space.
